summary: My favorite thing about Captain Marvel is that you’re watching it and you see that scene with Carol’s backstory and you have...
body: My favorite thing about Captain Marvel is that you’re watching it and you see that scene with Carol’s backstory and you have these fantastic shots with the explosion and a wonderful backstory and you think it’s the most beautiful thing you’ve ever seen when the next scene comes on with Carol having to deal with knowing this backstory and Maria, her best friend she didn’t know existed until less than 24 hours ago, comforts her and they hug and you realize that THAT was the most beautiful thing you’ve ever seen
